---
layout: base.njk
pagination:
  data: providerEntries
  size: 1
  alias: providerEntry
permalink: "/{{ providerEntry[0] }}/"
eleventyComputed:
  title: "{{ providerEntry[1].primaryCode }} - {{ providerEntry[1].codes[0].discount }} Off {{ providerEntry[1].name }} eSIM (Verified {{ buildTime | fmtDate('LLLL yyyy') }})"
  description: "✅ {{ providerEntry[1].primaryCode }}: {{ providerEntry[1].codes[0].discount }} off {{ providerEntry[1].name }} eSIM plans. Verified {{ buildTime | fmtDate('LLLL d, yyyy') }}. Save on travel data with tested codes."
  canonical: "{{ page.url | url | absoluteUrl(site.url) }}"
  providerKey: "{{ providerEntry[0] }}"
  provider: "{{ providerEntry[1] }}"
  ogImage: "{{ providerEntry[1].ogImage or '/assets/og-image.jpg' }}"
  modifiedISO: "{{ (providerEntry[1].codesLastUpdated or buildTime) | fmtISO }}"
  buildPretty: "{{ buildTime | fmtDate('LLLL d, yyyy') }}"
  renderFaq: true
---

{% set providerKey = providerEntry[0] %}
{% set provider = providerEntry[1] %}
{% set buildPretty = buildTime | fmtDate("LLLL d, yyyy") %}
{% set buildMonthYear = buildTime | fmtDate("LLLL yyyy") %}
{% set lastModISO = (provider.codesLastUpdated or buildTime) | fmtISO %}


<div class="provider-page" data-provider="{{ providerKey }}">
    <!-- Breadcrumbs for SEO and UX -->
    <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><span>{{ provider.name }} Discount Codes</span></li>
        </ol>
    </nav>

    <!-- Provider Header with Logo (for all pages) -->
    <header class="provider-header">
        <div class="provider-logo">
            {% if provider.logo %}
                <img src="{{ provider.logo }}" alt="{{ provider.name }} logo" class="logo" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';">
                <div class="logo-fallback" style="display: none;">{{ provider.name }}</div>
            {% else %}
                <div class="logo-fallback">{{ provider.name }}</div>
            {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h1>{{ provider.name }} Discount Codes</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">{{ provider.description }}</p>
    </header>

    {% if provider.codes and provider.codes.length > 0 %}
        <!-- Has Codes -->
        <section class="codes-section">
            <h2>Top {{ provider.name }} Discount Codes for {{ buildPretty }}</h2>

            
           {% for code in provider.codes %}
  {% set verifiedISO = (code.lastTested or provider.codesLastUpdated or buildTime) | fmtISO %}
  {% set verifiedPretty = (code.lastTested or provider.codesLastUpdated or buildTime) | fmtDate("LLLL d, yyyy") %}

  <div class="coupon-card {% if code.isPrimary %}primary-code{% endif %}">
    <div class="coupon-header">
      <h3>{{ code.discount }}</h3>
      {% if code.verified %}
      <span class="verified-badge">
        <i class="fas fa-circle-check" style="color:#10b981;"></i>
        <time class="last-reported {% if code.isPrimary %}primary-last-reported{% endif %}"
              datetime="{{ verifiedISO }}">Verified {{ verifiedPretty }}</time>
      </span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="coupon-code">
      <button class="copy-code-btn" data-code="{{ code.code }}">
        <i class="fas fa-copy"></i>
        <span class="code-text">{{ code.code }}</span>
        <span class="copy-label">Copy code</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <p class="coupon-description">{{ code.description }}</p>

    <div class="feedback-buttons">
      <button class="feedback-btn thumbs-up" data-feedback="up" title="This code worked!">
        <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up"></i>
      </button>
      <button class="feedback-btn thumbs-down" data-feedback="down" title="This code didn't work">
        <i class="fas fa-thumbs-down"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endfor %}


        </section>
{# About the verifier #}
<section id="about-verifier" class="verifier-about">
  <div class="verifier-media">
    <img
      src="/assets/profilepic.png"
      alt="David Wright, Coupon Researcher"
      class="verifier-avatar"
      loading="lazy"
      onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';"
    >
    <div class="verifier-avatar-fallback" style="display:none;" aria-hidden="true">DW</div>
  </div>

  <div class="verifier-copy">
    <h2 class="verifier-heading">About David Wright</h2>

    <p>I've been dragging a laptop around the world for 6 years straight. Originally from a London suburb you've definitely never heard of. I'm 34, technically homeless by choice, and have used more eSIM cards than most people have used napkins.</p>

    <h3>The stats</h3>
    <ul class="verifier-stats">
      <li>6 years of continuous travel</li>
      <li>52 countries and counting</li>
      <li>Every major eSIM provider tested (plus the sketchy ones)</li>
      <li>Zero tolerance for broken discount codes</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Why this exists</h3>
    <p>Got fed up with codes that don't work and affiliate sites full of lies. Every single code on this site gets manually tested before it goes live. No bots, no scraping, no hoping for the best.</p>

    <h3>My process</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Hunt codes in newsletters, apps, and checkout flows</li>
      <li>Test each one at actual checkout</li>
      <li>Remove expired codes immediately</li>
      <li>Update working percentages regularly</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>My approach</h3>
    <p>The codes work or they don't. Use them or don't. I'm not your customer service department. Check the privacy policy if you want to understand my communication style.</p>

    <h3>Probably irrelevant facts</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Can sleep through any airport announcement except gate changes</li>
      <li>Unreasonably angry about airline WiFi pricing</li>
      <li>Collects working discount codes like a digital hoarder</li>
      <li>Prefers debugging over small talk</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Don't contact me</h3>
    <p>I don't do support requests. The site works, the codes work, or they don't. Everything you need to know is already here.</p>

    <p><em>Currently in some airport lounge with overpriced coffee, making sure your next eSIM purchase costs less.</em></p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .verifier-about{display:grid;grid-template-columns:88px 1fr;gap:1rem;border:1px dashed #e5e7eb;background:#fafafa;padding:1rem;border-radius:10px;margin:1.25rem 0}
  .verifier-avatar{width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;object-fit:cover}
  .verifier-avatar-fallback{width:88px;height:88px;border-radius:9999px;background:#e5e7eb;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280}
  .verifier-heading{margin:.1rem 0 .25rem 0;font-size:1.125rem;font-weight:600}
  .verifier-copy h3{margin:.75rem 0 .25rem 0;font-size:1rem;font-weight:600}
  .verifier-copy p{margin:.25rem 0 .75rem 0;line-height:1.5}
  .verifier-copy ul{margin:.25rem 0 .75rem 0;padding-left:1rem}
  .verifier-copy li{margin:.15rem 0;line-height:1.4}
  .verifier-stats{list-style-type:none;padding-left:0}
  .verifier-stats li:before{content:"→ ";color:#6b7280;margin-right:0.25rem}
  @media (max-width:640px){
    .verifier-about{grid-template-columns:64px 1fr;gap:0.75rem}
    .verifier-avatar,.verifier-avatar-fallback{width:64px;height:64px}
  }
</style>


<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Person",
  "name": "David Wright",
  "image": "{{ '/assets/profilepic.png' | url | absoluteUrl(site.url) }}",
  "jobTitle": "Coupon Researcher",
  "description": "Finds and tests discount codes by hand. No AI. No scraping.",
  "worksFor": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "{{ site.title }}",
    "url": "{{ site.url }}"
  }
}
</script>


        <!-- Content Section (check for markdown files) -->
        <section class="content-section">
            {% include "content/" + providerKey + ".njk" %}
        </section>
        
    {% else %}
        <!-- Coming Soon -->
        <section class="coming-soon-section">
            <div class="coming-soon-content">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Coming Soon</h2>
                <p>We're working hard to bring you the best {{ provider.name }} discount codes and promo codes. Check back soon for verified codes that will save you money on your eSIM plans.</p>
                
                <div class="explore-section">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-compass"></i> Explore Other Providers</h3>
                    <p>While you wait, check out our verified discount codes for other eSIM providers:</p>
                    <div class="provider-links">
                        {% for key, otherProvider in codes %}
                            {% if otherProvider.codes and otherProvider.codes.length > 0 and key != providerKey %}
                            <a href="/{{ key }}" class="provider-link">
                                <span class="provider-name">{{ otherProvider.name }}</span>
                                <span class="provider-offer">Save with verified codes</span>
                            </a>
                            {% endif %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    {% endif %}
</div>